# Cloudflare Pages rewrites for zhimianxing-operation
# 1) Copy this file to public/_redirects
# 2) Replace YOUR_OPERATION_API_URL and YOUR_GM_API_URL with real public HTTPS URLs
#
# Example:
# /api/* https://zhimianxing-operation-api.onrender.com/api/:splat 200
# /gm/*  https://zhimianxing-gm-api.onrender.com/gm/:splat 200

/api/* https://YOUR_OPERATION_API_URL/api/:splat 200
/gm/*  https://YOUR_GM_API_URL/gm/:splat 200
